The council shall be composed of the following:
The secretary of the Kentucky Personnel Cabinet or the secretary's designee;
Three (3) members appointed by the President of the Senate, selected from a list of five (5) names submitted by each of the following organizations:
Associated Industries of Kentucky;
The Kentucky Chamber of Commerce; and
The Kentucky Chapter of the National Federation of Independent Business;
Three (3) members appointed by the Speaker of the House of Representatives, selected from a list of five (5) names submitted by each of the following organizations:
The Kentucky League of Cities;
The Kentucky Association of Counties; and
The Kentucky State AFL-CIO; and
One (1) member appointed by the Governor, selected from a list of five (5) names submitted by the Kentuckiana Chapter of Associated Builders and Contractors.
